<!-- Service Overview -->
<div class="service-overview-section">
<h2>About Our Vocational Expert Services</h2>
<p>Chris Skerritt provides CRC-certified vocational expert services throughout New England. Our vocational evaluations help attorneys quantify earning capacity losses in:</p>
<ul>
<li>Personal injury cases</li>
<li>Workers' compensation claims</li>
<li>Social Security disability matters</li>
<li>Long-term disability insurance disputes</li>
<li>Employment litigation</li>
</ul>
<p>Each city page provides location-specific information about local employment markets, major employers, and economic conditions that impact vocational assessments in that area.</p>
</div>
